{"tid":2462150,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登2024擬競選連任 預期和賀錦麗再度拍檔","createTime":"2021-03-25T23:32:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T04:47:26.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9144b24d4b849b116d0091064a764d6e474899","tid":2462150,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:32:14.000Z","msg":"（中央社華盛頓25日綜合外電報導）美國總統拜登今天舉行上任後首場記者會，他表示，他預期2024年將競選連任，並打算邀副總統賀錦麗繼續搭檔。<br />\n<br />\n外界始終有傳聞，現年78歲的拜登（Joe Biden）是否打算只當一任。拜登1月20日就任時，成為美國史上最高齡的總統。<br />\n<br />\n在被問到是否計劃競選連任時，拜登說：「我的回答是：是的，我打算競選連任，那是我的期望。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103260005.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202103260005.aspx&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GoVo%2BdRg%2Bg8pLLdQ7U%2BHcj8%3D&h=3da67a3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202103260005.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"afaefb3f861949a9843f3bf6e5105996cf4e650f","tid":2462150,"uid":3873,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:51:15.000Z","msg":"唔好講2024，你完埋今個任期先啦戀童祖<br />\n分分鐘條8婆頂你個位呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e430ec8ca2f18115b536112c72ae89e743e95b50","tid":2462150,"uid":265839,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:51:50.000Z","msg":"有咁長命先算啦"},{"pid":"0b8e7c3c732e512a7a975739cfbe50ec5152b2a5","tid":2462150,"uid":71335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:52:24.000Z","msg":"做得幾個月 就話想連任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba4c7f53b02bd227d64414f2a39f4190bb574bf","tid":2462150,"uid":208940,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-25T23:54:16.000Z","msg":"上天堂選舉？？選乜撚？上帝大哂喎"},{"pid":"fb502e8d97c07bdd12def5e039e3ac2804361d5c","tid":2462150,"uid":290393,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b8e7c3c732e512a7a975739cfbe50ec5152b2a5","tid":2